Love of my life, husband, soon to be baby daddy, BFF. I’m the luckiest gal in the world. 13 years of valentines with my David. ❤️

Happy birthday my baby 

Our gorgeous boy was born on February 24th at 11:37am weighing 6lb 2oz a week and a half early. 

Willem Cornelius Meisner, little Willie babe.

Trying not to wish away any of these precious newborn moments. Our sweet babe is 11days old today. With these gorgeous @lalo products arriving it’s hard not to imagine our sweet little buddy sitting in this darling high chair learning how to eat. 🥹 Thank you @lalo for creating a product that is both practical and beautiful. 🤍 #gifted #lalofam #shoplalo #lalo 

Feel free to use my affiliate link if you so choose 👼🏼🤍 www.meetlalo.com/tessadawn
We interrupt this newborn baby content for a pansy spotting.
He is risen!

Little baby Willie Cornelius is 6 months old today and had a banana to celebrate. I love you my angel bub! (And thank you, Billie Eilish, for the most sappy tear inducing song for us all to cry to)
…for friends and family 👐
Hoarding leftovers. Swipe for their shining moment. My return from mat leave/retirement kicked off this weekend 👐

The new @lalo x PAW Patrol collection is perfect for his growing skills while offering 100% non toxic materials, BPA free, food grade silicone and it’s cute as ever to boot. A little afternoon baking with @eliaelia.co baking mix. All you need is milk, eggs, and incorporate the entire bottle provided for you for the perfect amount of rich olive oil flavour. Dessert for dinner tonight?

If Christmas wasn’t already the best thing ever, try it with a baby. We were excited to use the @lalo tent conversion kit since our bub has outgrown his play gym. The pieces re-work into the cutest little tent without anything going to waste. Could we wait until Christmas? Absolutely NOT. #lalofam
